We just want to say a big thank you for watching the Mrbeast Parody, without you we won’t be able to do what we do. This is just the start, many more to come :)

This isn’t just my video, this is our video. I hold so many unforgettable memories from this shoot.Bhuvan bhai, thank you for stepping in as Titu Mama without a second thought. And Ashish, who had a packed day, still made time for this. Harsh, my brother, was the first to jump on board – I knew you'd be there. Kabita ma’am, your dedication between takes to nail the perfect shot was just inspiring.Nischay, despite not feeling well, still poured his heart into every scene (and let’s just say he might’ve enjoyed the "are bhenchod" line a bit too much). Mythpat with his wild horse expressions, ready to keep going even when we hit technical bumps for hours. Techno, the calmest one in the room. Mortal, who held onto that chicken for what must’ve been 12 takes – true dedication. Guruji, who patiently waited almost 12 hours in the vanity because we were running late. And Ranveer, bro, your acting was straight fire – "hahaha!"Abhishek, your dialogue delivery and reactions made every scene come alive; people don’t often realize how crucial that give-and-take energy is. Purav, bro, the best thing about you is how you completely surrender to each scene, bringing out its full potential. And the R2h boys – nothing needs to be said we died on set watching the fight hahah. Also I can't forget my favorite notyourtype badhiya dikhta hai ye sasta gian, see the last slide for his face reveal 😊Thank you to each and every one of you. This project wouldn’t be the same without you all. Legends, every single one 🫡
